-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
             International Standard Version -- http://isv.org/
     A project to typeset the ISV translation of the Bible using LaTeX.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

From the introduction:

"The Holy Bible: International Standard Version embodies the best results of
modern scholarship as to the meaning of Scripture, and it expresses this
meaning in clear and natural English. Produced by the ISV Foundation, the ISV
offers an exciting opportunity to read and study the Scriptures in a fresh,
new way."

Please see the LICENSE file for copyright and licensing details of the Bible
text itself. The main LaTeX template file and other scripts may be available
under other licenses as specified by their respective authors.
